1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
You have made it this far. Before you stands the final test.

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,500
Now we will discover whether you can react, move, and act as one team.

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:17,500
You must prevent the terminal lights from turning off for one full minute.

4
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:21,900
At the start, the screen will assign a color to each of your tokens.

5
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:27,000
That will be your color, and only you can respond when it appears.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:34,000
If a terminal lights up in your color, you must run to it and pass your token before the light disappears.

7
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:39,000
When you do, the terminal will immediately switch to a new color.

8
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Then a new sprint will begin for another person on the team.

9
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
If even one light goes out completely, you will fail.

10
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:54,000
You will need speed, constant focus, and nonstop movement.

11
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Hold out for one minute and the pyramid will be yours.
